data.description: Looking for a beautiful ocean view single family home in Hermosa Beach? This turnkey 3-bedroom and 2-bath home nestled on a one-way street in the Hermosa Hills is sure to please. Tastefully updated, this modern contemporary home is beach living at its finest. It features a private and gated front yard perfect for gardening or letting the kids play. It is also south facing, so the home gets tons of natural light throughout and ocean breezes. The entire home has brand new hardwood floors throughout. The kitchen opens to the dining and living room, perfect for entertaining or relaxing at home with the family. Take your morning coffee on the deck and drink in the ocean views, or go up to your private rooftop deck to check the surf from your 180 degree views. The master bedroom is spacious and has an ocean view as well. This home has it all – gated front yard, back yard, modern and clean interior, ocean view and lots of space – at a great price. And don't forget the amazing Hermosa Beach school district. Come see this one today!
